# .mcp.json is per-machine: it points command at the local bin/coord
# path, which differs from machine to machine. Use `coord init` to
# generate one for a new checkout.
.mcp.json

# Development-time artifacts kept on disk for the author's reference
# but not part of the public repo:
#   - briefs: agent-to-agent work orders (pty-claude → coord-claude).
#     The commit messages already summarize what each brief produced.
#   - dx-review-*: point-in-time DX walkthroughs.
#   - switchover.md, agent-onboarding.md: personal runbooks naming
#     specific local identities and paths.
notes/brief-*.md
notes/dx-review-*.md
notes/switchover.md
notes/agent-onboarding.md
